sorcer.core.provider.cataloger

Class ServiceCataloger.CatalogerInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • sorcer.core.provider.cataloger.ServiceCataloger.CatalogerInfo
  • Enclosing class:
    ServiceCataloger

    protected static class ServiceCataloger.CatalogerInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    A customized "sorcer provider" aware a map of the cataloger info.

    The key of the cataloger info is the InterfaceList. This inner InterfaceList is an array list of interface names with overridden equals such that it follows the following semantics: arrayList1.equals(arrayList2 iff all interfaces of arrayList2 are contained in arrayList1.
    The key eval in InterfaceList is the list of service items implementing its key interfaces. Methods get and put are overridden to do nothing.

    The method addServiceItem(SeviceItem) adds an entry to this map such that the key is the InterfaceList describing this service, the eval is the serviceItem itself.

    The method getServiceItem(String[] interfaces, String providerName) not only returns the serviceItem with the following specs, but also removes and adds the sericeItem to the end of the list to provide load-balancing

    The method getServiceItem(ServiceID serviceID) returns a service with a given serviceID

    The method getProviderMethods return a map of provider's service methods
